social_posts.post_text: When I saw @stoneyclover was doing a collab with @juicycouture I knew I had to get a piece (or three)! Juicy Couture was everything to me in high school. I wore the knee high socks to school with my uniform, my pencil case was a Juicy Couture makeup bag and I even named my first puppy Juicy Couture. She was a Yorkie/ chihuahua mix and the dogs remind me of her! 💕#bargainhuntingblonde

✨3 Relaxing Habits I Picked Up In 2022✨

I also find that working out helps me handle my stress as well but that’s much more of a time commitment than these 3! #bargainhuntingblonde

The @sezane archives sale has started with drop one! I love #sezane and it’s always nice to get their pieces on sale… but I will say everytime something goes wrong. So my top tips are: 
1- If you added something to your cart don’t delete it out of your cart- this will empty your entire cart and not just delete the item. 
2- Check the app and the website. Sometimes one will update quicker than the other and you will be able to snag an item.
3- If you see something you like pre archives buy it! The archives are older pieces and not everything makes it into the archives. So like this dress I loved last summer so I bought it because I didn’t want the stress of trying to find it during the archives 🤣#bargainhuntingblonde #sezanette #sezanearchives
